ProMED-mail
e-mail: promed@promedmail.org
[The causative agent mentioned in this report is a hantavirus causing
hemorrhagic fever with renal syndrome (HFRS), the Russian name of which is
Gemorragicheskaya Lihoradka s Pochechnym Sindromom, or in abbreviated form
GLPS. - Mod.AV
